nodes.text: Swamp rancor was a sub-species of Rancor living in swamps. Their notable difference from common rancors were the two large horns on their head, as well as a darker shade of skin. They could be found in the Endless Swamp on Zakuul, the capital world of the Eternal Empire.
Swamp rancors appear in Star Wars: The Old Republic: Knights of the Fallen Empire in the Zakuul swamp.
